## 1. Purpose

This document explains how OPRMT™ repository materials may be used in personal, educational, internal business, and commercial contexts.

The purpose of this guidance is to protect the integrity of the OPRMT™ Framework while allowing legitimate learning, reference, implementation, and approved business use.

This document is guidance only. It does not replace the repository `LICENSE.md`, `NOTICE.md`, `TERMS.md`, or any signed agreement with the owner.

