## 8. Commercial Use Decision Guide

Use this guide to determine whether permission is likely needed.

| Question | If Yes | Permission Likely Needed |
|---|---|---|
| Are you selling access to OPRMT™ materials? | Commercial sale | Yes |
| Are you including OPRMT™ files in a paid product? | Redistribution | Yes |
| Are you rebranding OPRMT™ as your own system? | White-label use | Yes |
| Are you using OPRMT™ branding in client work? | Commercial service | Review required |
| Are you claiming official certification authority? | Certification claim | Yes |
| Are you only studying the materials privately? | Personal use | Usually no |
| Are you citing the repository with attribution? | Public reference | Usually no |
| Are you using the structure internally without redistribution? | Internal use | Usually no |

